First Lady Melania Trump visited the Dove School of Discovery Elementary School in Tulsa, Oklahoma as part of her Be Best initiative. The school, which received the 2018 National School of Character Award, focuses on character development and integrates parents into the curriculum through workshops. Mrs. Trump visited three different classrooms, engaging with students and observing their teamwork and communication skills. She emphasized the importance of character-based education and praised the school for its emphasis on kindness, respect, and positive interactions.